title: Designmoo
description: Designmoo is widely recognized within the design community for its distinctive color palette. The brand embraces a vibrant shade of red, symbolized by the hex code E64B50, and a contrasting warm yellow represented by the hex code DBC65D. These colors are prominently displayed across various design platforms, including their Dribbble tag, enhancing brand visibility and establishing a memorable visual identity in the design industry.
